HEADWORD: Sephen
<hw>Se"phen</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
large sting ray of the genus <gen>Trygon</gen>, especially <spn>Trygon
sephen</spn> of the Indian Ocean and the Red Sea. The skin is an article
of commerce.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sepia</ent>⟦br⟧
